```&lt;iframe class="rsk-iframe-module" src="{{ module.source_url }}" width="{{ module.iframe_width }}" height="{{ module.iframe_height }}" frameborder="0" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;```

```.rsk-iframe-module {
  max-width: 90vw;
  max-height: 70vh;
  display: block;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
@media only screen and (max-device-width: 768px) {
  .rsk-iframe-module {
    max-height: 50vh;
  }
}```
